Breaking Bad...</i>

00:07.113 --> 00:10.277
- You're so strong today!
- Marie, get out.

00:11.444 --> 00:13.834
I'm going to work.
Keep this party going!

00:13.913 --> 00:19.281
Walter White wants to buy my car wash,
the price he pays is 20 million dollars.

00:20.718 --> 00:23.419
He cuts a man's throat
just to send a message?

00:23.531 --> 00:25.538
Get me in a room with him.

00:25.857 --> 00:27.000
You're done?

